Title: St. Patrick's Day
Plot: Jack feels unworthy of his latest award and attempts to redeem himself by taking on the writers in a strategic board game. Liz believes she's cursed on St. Patrick's Day when her ex-boyfriend Dennis shows up to derail her relationship with Criss. Meanwhile, Hazel struggles to keep the peace between Tracy and Jenna.
GuestStars: James Marsden, Dean Winters, Kristen Schaal, Al Roker, Bernie McInerney, Ira Glass, Sue Galloway
